RecipeManagementSystem/
│
├── src/
│   ├── dao/                      # Data Access Object (DAO) Layer
│   ├── model/                    # Model classes (Data Objects)
│   ├── servlet/                  # Servlet classes (Controller layer)
│   ├── service/                  # Service Layer (Business Logic)
│   ├── util/                     # Utility classes (e.g., DB connection)
│   └── web/                      # Web resources (JSP, CSS, JS)
│       ├── WEB-INF/
│       │   ├── lib/              # Libraries (JAR files)
│       │   ├── classes/          # Compiled Java classes
│       │   ├── jsp/              # JSP files (views)
│       │   └── web.xml           # Web configuration file (Deployment descriptor)
│       └── index.jsp             # Entry point JSP
├── lib/                          # External libraries (third-party JARs)
├── pom.xml                       # Maven configuration file (for dependencies)
├── .gitignore                    # Git ignore configuration
└── README.md                     # Project documentation
